    "Like InceptionTime, H-InceptionTime is an ensemble of five base models.",
    "To avoid the need to find the best length of hand-crafted filters, H-InceptionTime chooses different lengths for each hand-crafted filter and used all of them.",
    "They found H-InceptionTime provided a small, but significant, improvement over InceptionTime on the 112 UCR datasets.",
    "Both ResNet and Inception have approximately 500k trainable parameters and are computationally intensive.",
    "In 2023, Ismail-Fawaz et al. (2023b) proposed a smaller model for InceptionTime, called Light Inception with boosTing tEchniques (LITE)."
